Interface DatabindView

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Binder, DatabindValidationHandler, HasDatabindUiHandler, HasDatabindValues, WidgetBinder
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DatabindViewImpl

    public interface DatabindView
extends HasDatabindUiHandler, HasDatabindValues, WidgetBinder, DatabindValidationHandler
    Interface that must be implemented by the View to support databind. Usually you will delegate all possible executions to DatabindViewEngine.
